      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Aug 3 obituary of Grand Rabbi Shlomo Halberstam of the Bobover sect included an incomplete reference to members of his family who survived Holocaust</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The obituary of Grand Rabbi Shlomo Halberstam of the Bobover sect yesterday included an incomplete reference from family friends to the members of his family who survived the Holocaust. Although several relatives were killed, his mother, a brother and six sisters -- not just his eldest son -- survived.</p>
      </block>
